               ragel (>=6.8),
               po-debconf,
               pkg-config
Standards-Version: 5.0.0
Homepage: https://www.hyperscan.io

Package: openresty-plus-hyperscan
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Pre-Depends: debconf, libstdc++6
Description: High-performance regular expression matching library for OpenResty Plus
 Hyperscan for OpenResty Plus is a high-performance multiple regex matching library. It
 follows the regular expression syntax of the commonly-used libpcre
 library, but is a standalone library with its own C API.

Package: openresty-plus-hyperscan-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, openresty-plus-hyperscan
Description: Libraries and header files for the hyperscan library of OpenResty Plus
 Hyperscan for OpenResty Plus is a high-performance multiple regex matching library. It
 follows the regular expression syntax of the commonly-used libpcre
 library, but is a standalone library with its own C API.
 .
 This package provides the libraries, include files and other resources
 needed for developing Hyperscan applications.

